personal-blog
base full-stack personal blog program A personal blog system built with a Go + Gin backend and Vue 3 + TypeScript frontend.

Project Overview
Personal Blog is a fully-featured personal blogging platform supporting article management, comment systems, user management, feedback systems, and more. The backend is built with Go and the Gin framework, while the frontend uses Vue 3 and TypeScript. Data storage integrates MySQL, Redis, and Elasticsearch.

Technology Stack
Backend
Language: Go
Framework: Gin
Database: MySQL
Cache: Redis
Search Engine: Elasticsearch
Image Storage: Local storage or Qiniu Cloud
Authentication: JWT
Frontend
Framework: Vue 3
Language: TypeScript
State Management: Pinia
Build Tool: Vite
