Quick Start
Backend Configuration
Install Go dependencies:
cd server
go mod tidy
Configure config.yaml:
system:
addr: :8080
storage: local  # or qiniu
mysql: host: localhost port: 3306 dbname: blog username: root password: your_password

redis: host: localhost port: 6379

jwt: secret: your_secret_key expire: 7200

qiniu: access_key: your_access_key secret_key: your_secret_key bucket: your_bucket domain: your_domain

3. Initialize the database:
```bash
go run . --sql
Create an admin account:
go run . --admin
Start the server:
go run .
Frontend Configuration
Install dependencies:
cd web
npm install
Configure environment variables (.env):
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080
Start the development server:
npm run dev
Build for production:
npm run build
Command-Line Tools
The backend provides the following command-line flags:

--sql: Initialize MySQL database tables
--sql-export: Export database SQL to file
--sql-import: Import SQL data from file
--es: Initialize Elasticsearch indexes
--es-export: Export Elasticsearch data
--es-import: Import data into Elasticsearch
--admin: Create an admin account
API Overview
Base APIs
POST /api/base/captcha - Get CAPTCHA
POST /api/base/email - Send email verification code
User APIs
POST /api/user/register - Register user
POST /api/user/login - Login user
POST /api/user/email_login - Login via email
GET /api/user/info - Get user information
PUT /api/user/info - Update user information
Article APIs
GET /api/article/list - Get article list
GET /api/article/search - Search articles
POST /api/article/create - Create article
PUT /api/article/update - Update article
DELETE /api/article/delete - Delete article
Comment APIs
GET /api/comment/list - Get comment list
POST /api/comment/create - Create comment
DELETE /api/comment/delete - Delete comment
Website Configuration APIs
GET /api/website/info - Get website info
GET /api/website/carousel - Get carousel images
PUT /api/website/carousel - Update carousel images
